<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">近日，一场别开生面的徒步活动在风景如画的先锋小镇成功举行。活动旨在通过徒步的方式，让参与者们在领略自然风光的同时，深入了解邓禹将军这位历史人物事迹和将军岭丰富的历史文化，共同探索生态保护与人文历史之间的和谐共生之道。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">这也是江西软件职业技术大学师生与蜉蝣户外俱乐部成员共同开启的一场别开生面的“见山也拾山”公益净山徒步活动，为生态文明作贡献。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-28%2021%3A05%3A19%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2032261519&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=GjS2G%2FKkDjIHGu24ndF0kFzosis%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">大家怀揣着对大自然的敬畏与热爱，踏上了徒步的征程，呼吸着清新的空气，享受着与自然和谐共处的快乐。在徒步过程中，大家历经了将军岭、马蹄石等历史遗址，了解了邓禹将军这位历史人物的英雄事迹。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">除了领略自然风光和历史文化，活动还注重倡导环保理念。生态文明志愿者们向大家普及环保知识，倡导大家爱护自然、保护环境。同时，活动还采取了多项环保措施，如：沿途捡起每一片垃圾、减少一次性用品的使用、分类回收垃圾等，以实际行动践行绿色出行、低碳生活的理念。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-28%2021%3A06%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2032261566&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=iqUIbXMn7a3Vpf%2FQ7FKfKIXDIis%3D" alt="" width="650" height="375" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">据悉，东汉初年，邓禹将军（东汉云台28将之首）奉刘秀之命，平定江南，率部在豫章罗亭岭口与叛军蔡宏采用诱敌深入谋略，打了一场以少胜多的歼灭战。后人为了纪念邓禹大将军的这次“上马蹄还是下马蹄”的智慧之战，将许多战斗遗迹加上神秘的传说世代保留了下来。后人把这次战斗的山岭叫“将军岭”，现今将军岭山顶上有一块形似马蹄的天然石头，这块可俯瞰山下的天然石头叫“马蹄石”。此外，还有“万弩岩”“万弩桥”等历史遗址的传说。在将军岭山顶，可观望到先锋小镇及软件大学校园，校园内正活跃着上万名“学好软件，报效祖国”莘莘学子，将军岭以其常看常新的历史英姿，陪伴着软件大学的学子们成长成才。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-29%2008%3A28%3A0121.png?Expires=2032302481&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=wKopItJ%2Fqqqh7V52SAyq8gfj2K4%3D" alt="" width="650" height="355" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">在先锋小镇，学校师生参与建设花园式生态文明校园。自2019年开始，学校每年举办春季郁金香花展和秋季金秋花展，学生们在有经验的老师带领下，亲手栽培花卉、设计花卉造型，参与每年春秋两次花展的全过程。每次花展都吸引了许多游客和团体前来观赏，网红们也组团前来打卡。师生们在优美的生态环境中学习、工作和生活，用良好的生态文化氛围陶冶自己。</span></p>